Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.21,0:00:07.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Quill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.53,0:00:09.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:11.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Parchment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:12.07,Spike,,0,0,0,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:12.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Extra ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:13.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:14.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Extra-extra ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.07,0:00:15.70,Spike,,0,0,0,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:17.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Is that everything on the checklist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:18.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.73,0:00:19.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:22.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Now that we've completed the checklist of things we need to create a checklist,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.67,0:00:25.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,we can make my checklist of the things I have to get done by the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:27.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.65,0:00:28.31,Spike,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:29.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Item
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:32.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Create checklist of the things I have to accomplish by the end of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:20.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How are we doing, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.47,0:01:21.34,Spike,,0,0,0,,Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.42,0:01:23.38,Spike,,0,0,0,,We've already dropped off your cape at the cleaner's…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.44,0:01:25.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,…returned the blackboard you borrowed from Cheerilee…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.30,0:01:27.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,…ordered new parchment and quills from the stationery shop…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:31.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Seems like we just placed an order for those a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:35.00,Spike,,0,0,0,,Can't imagine why we go through so many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:37.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sounds like we're ahead of schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:37.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:39.94,Spike,,0,0,0,,Cupcakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.73,0:01:46.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I only ordered twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.70,0:01:48.06,MrsCake,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.22,0:01:51.67,MrsCake,,0,0,0,,But I had an extra, so I thought I'd make it a baker's dozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:55.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, that was very thoughtful of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:58.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's just some of the icing from the extra cupcake
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:00.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,is getting all over the one next to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:00.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:03.14,MrsCake,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:04.12,MrsCake,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.30,0:02:06.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's just that I'm planning on sharing these at a picnic later
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:09.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and I don't want anypony to feel like somepony else is getting more icing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.09,0:02:13.64,MrsCake,,0,0,0,,Oh… no, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:15.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:17.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'll just move some of this one to…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:20.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think I may have scooped too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:23.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oops! Now those two have more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:25.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Let's just try this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:29.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No, that won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:30.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Let me just…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:32.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…put some here, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:34.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No, that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.87,0:02:36.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A little more on this one…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…a little bit… and wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:38.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'll just…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.61,0:02:39.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Ooh, a little bit here…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:41.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…and here…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:41.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…and…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:43.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:46.60,MrsCake,,0,0,0,,Hmm, oh, yes. Much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:49.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay! Time to tackle the next item on our…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:50.52,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:54.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're gonna have to add "Give a baby dragon a bath" to our list.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:02:59.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Very efficient!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And a little bit gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:04.85,Spike,,0,0,0,,Looks like that's everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:06.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Almost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.03,0:03:10.34,Spike,,0,0,0,,"Triple-check checklist to make sure we didn't miss anything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:12.53,Spike,,0,0,0,,when we double-checked the checklist."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:14.06,Spike,,0,0,0,,Check.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:19.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,I've been holding that quill so long, I've got a claw cramp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:24.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, good thing we don't have anything to report to Princess Celestia this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.10,Spike,,0,0,0,,I don't think I could write another word.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:29.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We haven't sent a letter to Princess Celestia this week?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:29.90,Spike,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:30.86,Spike,,0,0,0,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:31.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Bad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:32.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,BAD?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:33.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Of course it's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:36.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to send Princess Celestia a letter every week
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:38.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,telling her about a lesson I've learned about friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.33,0:03:39.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Not every other week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:40.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Not every ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:42.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Every! Single! Week!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Where's my calendar?! Where's my calendar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:48.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,Where it… always is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:51.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,When did we send the last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:54.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,Last… Tuesday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:56.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And today is…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.10,0:03:57.79,Spike,,0,0,0,,Tuesday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:00.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No-no-no-no-no-no-no-no…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:04.61,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If I don't send her a letter by sundown, I'll be…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:07.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,TARDY!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:09.74,Spike,,0,0,0,,What's that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Tar-dy, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.09,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Late! I'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, how could I've let this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm usually so organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've never been late for an assignment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:19.97,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.17,0:04:21.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,You're the most studious student ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:24.99,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the Princess will forgive you if you miss one little deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:26.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid to take that chance, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:30.16,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is the ruler of all of Equestria we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:32.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The pony who holds my fate in her hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:35.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What if she doesn't forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:36.93,Spike,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't think she…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.22,0:04:38.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What if instead she starts thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:40.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm not taking my studies on friendship seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:41.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,Why would she…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:44.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What if she makes me come back to Canterlot and puts me back in school
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:47.75,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and makes me *prove* I've been taking them seriously by giving me a test?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What if I don't pass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,But why wouldn't you pass…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:52.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She's my teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.94,0:04:55.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Do you know what teachers do to students who don't pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.89,0:04:58.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,THEY SEND THEM BACK A GRADE!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.26,0:05:00.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But she won't just send me back a grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:02.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She'll send me back to…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:04.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…magic kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:12.83,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:14.87,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:18.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,That is the most ridiculous thing I've ever heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.74,0:05:21.43,Spike,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna be sent back to magic kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:22.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:24.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I have no reason to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:27.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Because I'm going to solve a friend's problem
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:30.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and get that letter to Princess Celestia before sundown!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:32.58,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.98,0:05:35.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Got any problems, troubles, conundrums or any other sort of issues
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:38.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,major or minor, that I as a good friend could help you solve?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.06,Spike,,0,0,0,,I got nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:50.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Then it looks like I'm gonna have to find somepony who does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:53.90,Spike,,0,0,0,,This won't end well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:00.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You've got this, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:03.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You still have plenty of time to get that letter to Princess Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.81,0:06:07.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Has to be somepony around here who needs the help of a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:09.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:14.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:16.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:17.87,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:22.09,Rarity,,0,0,0,,WHY, WHY, WHY?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:25.22,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Of all the worst things that could happen, this is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:28.13,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The! Worst! Possible! Thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:31.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What's happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.23,0:06:36.40,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I've lost my diamond-encrusted purple ribbon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.03,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I have searched HIGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:39.41,Rarity,,0,0,0,,And I have searched low.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:40.14,Rarity,,0,0,0,,LOW AND HIGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:40.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,High and low.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.33,Rarity,,0,0,0,,But I can't find it anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:46.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,ANYWHERE!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:51.26,Rarity,,0,0,0,,How can I possibly finish my latest creation if I can't find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.87,0:06:53.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Never fear, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,As your friend\NI'll do my best to help you fi…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:56.63,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Oh, there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:59.34,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Isn't it always just the last place you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:04.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So you just lost your ribbon…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:08.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…but now you've found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:08.91,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And nothing else is bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:14.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Nothing that I as a good friend could help you with?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:18.86,Rarity,,0,0,0,,There is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:20.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,YES?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:23.07,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I think I've left my measuring tape under the fabric over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:24.32,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Could you get that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:28.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Measuring tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:29.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.03,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Twilight. Is there something bother…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:33.96,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:39.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No need to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rarity is just one pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm sure one of my other friends will need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.88,0:08:03.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What in the world…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.90,0:08:07.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow must be angry with Applejack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She must hate her guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.39,0:08:10.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.52,0:08:13.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:15.96,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Listen, Rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:18.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know you're upset with Applejack, but don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:21.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is that has come between you two,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:25.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that I as a good friend can help you resolve your problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.40,0:08:29.16,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Uh, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.76,0:08:31.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:33.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You don't have to hide your feelings from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can tell you two must have had a terrible fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:41.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Now, why don't you tell me all about your issues with Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.39,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,I don't have any issues with Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:44.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:46.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Then why are you destroying her property?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.39,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Because she asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:49.69,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Right, Applejack?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:50.94,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.14,0:08:54.38,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I wanted to put up a new barn, but this one's gotta come down first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:56.49,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Now get back to it, RD.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:58.28,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,You got it, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.59,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,I'd take cover if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:29.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I've wasted all that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:30.95,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I should have just come here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:34.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy always has some fear she's trying to get over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:36.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,As a good friend I'll be able to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:09:59.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How can this be happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:02.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Of all the days she had to stop being such a scaredy-pony she had to pick today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.15,0:10:05.01,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:08.53,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You really should have come to me sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:12.03,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,You were carrying so much tension in that shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:18.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It'll all be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:19.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The day isn't over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:21.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But it will be over soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:25.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It'll be all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.13,0:10:27.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My time in Ponyville, my advanced studies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.80,0:10:29.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No, no. You're a good student.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:30.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.53,0:10:33.12,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh! But what if I can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:35.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You can! You just have to keep it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:36.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Keep! It! Together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:40.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,Are you talking to… yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.80,0:10:42.63,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.11,Spike,,0,0,0,,Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:56.11,Spike,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:01.41,Spike,,0,0,0,,Twilight, I'm really worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:03.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,I mean this letter thing is really getting to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:04.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:07.74,Spike,,0,0,0,,You've been so anxious all day that you've completely forgot about the picnic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:10.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just relax and go hang out with…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:11.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The picnic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:14.15,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I should go see my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:15.98,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you've come to your senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:28.01,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Please tell me I did not forget the plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:28.94,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:30.48,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I totally forgot them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:33.49,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Of all the worst things that could happen, this is…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:36.69,Rarity,,0,0,0,,The! Worst! Possible! Thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:41.07,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Why, why, why!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:44.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.86,0:11:47.03,Rarity,,0,0,0,,You didn't expect me to lay on the grass, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.25,0:11:57.24,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,You all right, hun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:57.99,Twilight,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I am not all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.65,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's just terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:05.37,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:06.83,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Simply awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.45,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:10.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,It's the most terrific trouble I've ever been in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:13.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,and I really, really, really need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.79,0:12:14.72,Somepony,,0,0,0,,YES?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My letter to Princess Celestia is almost overdue!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.17,0:12:20.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And I haven't learned anything about friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.94,0:12:23.98,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:26.05,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,I thought something really awful had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:30.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Something awful HAS happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:34.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If I don't turn in the letter on time, I'll be tardy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:36.72,Twilight,,0,0,0,,TAAARDY!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.42,0:12:42.70,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,No offense, sugarcube,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:46.06,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,but it looks like somepony's gettin' themselves all worked up over nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:47.76,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is not nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.93,0:12:49.30,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:52.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I need you guys to help me find somepony with a problem I can fix before sundown!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:55.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My whole life depends on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:59.20,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh, Twilight. You're such a crackup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:01.62,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Come on, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:04.12,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Have a seat and stop sweatin' small stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:11.26,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Wow, I've never seen Twilight so upset before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:14.10,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Ugh, what a drama queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:17.02,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Relatively speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:22.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Clock is ticking, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.29,0:13:25.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Clock… is… ticking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:27.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Keep it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:31.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If I can't find a friendship problem…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…I'll make a friendship problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:54.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hi, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:57.38,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Hi, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:13:58.30,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,How's it goi..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:13:59.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Great! Just great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:02.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You three look like you're doing great too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Looks like three good friends who obviously
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.42,0:14:07.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,don't need the help of another good friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:11.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is Smarty Pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:12.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She was mine when I was your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.01,0:14:15.35,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And now I want to give her to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:19.34,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Uh… She's… great!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.64,0:14:21.89,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Yeah… Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:26.19,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I really like her… mane?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:29.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,She even comes with her own notebook and quill!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:33.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,For when you want to pretend she's doing her homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.14,0:14:36.81,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,That's, um… great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.15,0:14:39.43,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Yeah… Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.21,0:14:44.34,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I really like her… mane?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:47.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I just hope the fact that there are three of you…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:49.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…and only one of her doesn't become a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:53.21,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'd hate to cause a rift between such good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.52,0:14:56.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,So who wants to play with her first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:59.05,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You should play with her first, Sweetie Belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:01.50,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,You know, cause you like her mane so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:03.13,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,No-no-no-no-no-no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:06.16,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I think Scootaloo should get to play with her first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:09.60,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I'd love to, but… You take her, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:13.08,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Applejack says it's important to share.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I got to think of something. Think-think-think-think-think, Twilight, think!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.45,0:15:18.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:21.69,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Ooh, you're going to like Smarty Pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:24.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And you're going to like her more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:34.49,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.53,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:38.68,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I really like her mane!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:43.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The "want it, need it" spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.26,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Works every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. Let's break it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.45,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I think you can all see that there is an important lesson…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:50.74,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…to be learned here about…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:54.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come on, girls. We're all friends here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:56.36,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Don't you think you have to share?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.49,0:15:58.22,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.49,0:16:06.46,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Big McIntosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.86,0:16:07.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:10.33,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You gotta help me get that doll away from those girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:12.18,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Eeyup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:20.93,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.36,0:16:23.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Now if you could just give her to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:24.96,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Nnnope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:27.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:28.67,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Give her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:33.50,Mayor,,0,0,0,,What's all the commotion about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.10,Somepony,,0,0,0,,They're fighting over that doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:37.78,Somepony,,0,0,0,,That incredible, amazing doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:42.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Can't get a clear shot…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:48.44,Mayor,,0,0,0,,Give me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:54.45,BigMac,,0,0,0,,Nnnope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:16:57.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, what have I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:05.56,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Y'all hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:12.30,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What in the name of all things oats 'n apples is goin' on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:20.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,DON'T LOOK AT IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:22.44,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Don't look at what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.60,0:17:23.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,My Smarty Pants doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:26.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I enchanted her and now everypony is fighting over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.78,0:17:29.82,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Why would you enchant your doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.96,0:17:31.28,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, I had to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:33.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I had nothing to report to Princess Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.69,0:17:36.85,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I thought if I couldn't find a problem, I'd make a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:38.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,The day is almost over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:40.44,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Not almost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:48.26,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:53.10,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Whoa, Nelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:25.58,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Meet me in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:29.10,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Goodbye, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:30.82,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If you care to visit…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.48,0:18:33.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…I'll be in a magic kindergarten…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:35.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,…back in Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:38.90,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Magic kindergarten?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.04,0:18:39.98,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,Canterlot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:43.13,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,We're never gonna see Twilight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:45.60,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do, y'all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.16,0:18:48.50,Rarity,,0,0,0,,Of all the worst things that could happen…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:52.48,Rarity,,0,0,0,,…this is the! Worst! Possible! Thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:57.46,Rarity,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.66,0:18:59.00,Rarity,,0,0,0,,I really mean it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:04.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But… but… I'm supposed to send you a letter about friendship every week.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:06.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I missed the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:07.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm a bad student.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:09.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm… tardy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.58,0:19:12.97,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You are a wonderful student, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:15.57,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I don't have to get a letter every week to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:16.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:20.53,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,WAIT!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.85,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,You can't punish her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:23.19,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,It wasn't her fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:24.40,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:25.54,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Please, your highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:27.20,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,We all saw that Twilight was upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.36,0:19:29.51,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,But we thought that the thing she was worrying about
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:31.09,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,wasn't worth worrying about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.40,0:19:33.12,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,So when she ran out all worked up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:35.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,not a single one of us tried to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:38.08,Rarity,,0,0,0,,As Twilight's good friends, we should have taken
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.09,0:19:40.59,Rarity,,0,0,0,,her feelings seriously and been there for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:42.51,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,Please don't take her away from us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.55,0:19:44.90,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,just because we were too insensitive to help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.82,0:19:50.73,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Looks like you all learned a pretty valuable lesson today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:57.90,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Very well. I'll forget Twilight's punishment on one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:03.16,Celestia,,0,0,0,,From this day forth I would like you all
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:06.07,Celestia,,0,0,0,,to report to me your findings on the magic of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.14,Celestia,,0,0,0,,When and only when you happen to discover them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:14.94,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.49,0:20:17.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,How did you know I was in trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:19.10,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Your friend Spike made me aware
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:21.14,Celestia,,0,0,0,,that you were letting your fears get the best of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.54,0:20:24.21,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I commend him for taking your feelings seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:28.18,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Now, if you will all excuse me, I must return to Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.74,0:20:30.38,Celestia,,0,0,0,,I'm expecting some mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:36.32,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Y'all heard the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:37.93,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,Spike, take a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.58,0:20:46.20,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,"Dear Princess Celestia."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:50.05,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,"We're writin' to you because today we all learned a little somethin' about friendship."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:53.23,FlutterShy,,0,0,0,,"We learned that you should take your friends' worries seriously."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:56.26,RainbowDash,,0,0,0,,"Even if you don't think that she has anything to worry about."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:20:59.57,Rarity,,0,0,0,,"And that you shouldn't let your worries turn a small problem…"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:02.91,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"…into an enormously huge entire-town-in-total-chaos…"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:05.32,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,"…Princess-has-to-come-and-save-the-day problem!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.79,0:21:08.18,AppleJack,,0,0,0,,"Signed, your loyal subjects."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.98,0:21:12.83,Spike,,0,0,0,,"PS. Obviously Spike did not have to learn a lesson…"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:16.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,"…because he is the best, most awesome friend a pony could ask for."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:19.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,"Unlike everypony else, he took things seriously. And…"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:23.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,Uh… Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.61,0:21:24.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'll just, um…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,SCHASTLIVY PONETC
